Class ProductContainer

java.lang.Object
  model.common.Model
      model.productcontainer.ProductContainer

java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<IModel>, IModel
Direct Known Subclasses:
ProductGroup, StorageUnit
public class ProductContainer
extends Model

The ProductContainer is the base class for ProductGroup and for StorageUnit. It defines the shared interface for these objects.

Field Detail

_rootParentId

protected int _rootParentId
A unique ID is associated with every ProductContainer once it is presisted to the vault. _id is not set by the user, but by the vault when it is saved. _id can be -1 if it is new and has not been saved
